Package: correspondenceTables
Type: Package
Title: Functions for creating or updating correspondence tables between two statistical classifications
Date: 2022-09-21
Version: 0.7.1
Authors@R: c(person("Vasilis", "Chasiotis", role = "aut", comment="Department of Statistics, Athens University of Economics and Business"), 
      person("Photis", "Stavropoulos", role = "aut", comment="Quantos S.A. Statistics and Information Systems"),
      person("Martin", "Karlberg", role = "ctb"),
      person("Mátyás", "Mészáros", email = "matyas.meszaros@ec.europa.eu", role = "cre"))
Description: The package contains two functions.
    One function updates the correspondence table between two statistical classifications when one of the classifications gets updated to a new version.
    The other function creates a candidate correspondence table between two classifications when there are correspondence tables leading from the first classification to the second one via intermediate ''pivot'' classifications. 
